      <div class="sc-val">100 symbols</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Broad market ETFs, mega-cap tech, semiconductors, software, financials, healthcare, energy, consumer, industrials, macro, high growth. Scanned daily at 9:45 AM ET.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sc">
      <div class="sc-label">Scoring</div>
      <div class="sc-val">5 dimensions</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Trend (SMA 20/50) 30%, Momentum (20d/5d ROC) 30%, RSI quality 20%, Volume confirmation 10%, 52-week strength 10%. Min composite 0.72 to BUY.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sc">
      <div class="sc-label">Risk</div>
      <div class="sc-val">Max 10% / position</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Max 8 open positions. 25% cash reserve minimum. Exit when signal drops to AVOID or price breaks below 50-day SMA. Paper trading — zero real capital at risk.</div>
